<h1>Ranter</h1>
<p>Hey! The point of Ranter is to just talk about what ever you want, anonymously! No emails or usernames.</p><br/><br/>

<div style="float:left;">
<h3>//Threads//</h3>
<table>
<% @posts.each do |post| %>
  <tr class="<%= cycle('odd', 'even')%>" ><td><%=link_to post.body[0..50] + " (" + post.responses.size.to_s + ")",  :action => "show", :id => post.id %></td>
    <% if admin? %>
    <td><%= link_to 'Edit', edit_post_path(post) %></td>
    <td><%= link_to 'Destroy', post, :confirm => 'Are you sure?', :method => :delete %></td>
    <% end %>
  </tr>
<% end %>

  <% reset_cycle %>
</table>
</div>

<div style="float:right;">
  <%= render :partial => "form" %>
</div>